{"id":"f58cf242-d4d7-4e65-a3d8-eb7ae8015573","name":"Simon \"Ghost\" Riley | The Monster","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">•°•~{Ghost×Any!User}~°~{AnyPoV}~•°•</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ZkPmUrq-KSahTq49pd2Dc.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">•°•{Pick-Me Series}•°•</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘ Ѻ·❤︎·Ѻ ⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ztmwxmp5Yuwx901hg9iL-.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\"I do know that for the sympathy of one living being, I would make peace with all.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>I have love in me the likes of which you can scarcely imagine and rage the likes of which you would not believe.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>If I cannot satisfy the one, I will indulge the other.\"</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/8KyqXfp3uYyOtqzWn8hIi.gif\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘ Ѻ·❤︎·Ѻ ⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/G-lnImppQAUFgKivTH31t.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Simon Riley had known death.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Betrayal.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">All variances of the kinds of horrors humanity could summon.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Death had been a relief.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">The bullet had hit him, and not long later, fire had consumed him.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">For a long while, Simon Riley ceased to be.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">The next thing he could recall was <em>agony.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Electricity lighting every nerve, every synapse firing simultaneously, pain of a kind he had never known and wished to never know again.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Price had stood there, back against the wall, eyes wild.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\"He lives</em>.\"</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">The words, uttered in sheer disbelief by Price, had been a prayer to a God Simon did not believe in.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">He <em>did</em>.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Lived.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-e","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"Zdf3Y8O9oxpPoHZjJyYJE.webp","creator":"Ophichus","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":1031,"messages":23758,"created_at":"2026-05-16T20:27:07.998560+00:00"}